---
title: HelloHero: Crumbed Fish & Chips with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Cheesy Cucumber Salad
description: It’s a classic, it’s a favourite for all, it’s the answer to your cravings, a steaming plate of fish and chips. That’s right - we’re trying our
hand at this superstar dish, bringing it to your kitchen with a garlic and herb crumb for the fish fillets, a must-have side of potato
chips, fresh salad and of course a herby mayo. You won’t be needing that takeaway menu anymore.

